These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
Pet: turtle, goldfish, chinchilla, horse
Beverage: sprite, mirinda, water, almond-milk
House: gothic-revival, farmhouse, colonial, ranch-style
Nationality: american, italian, malaysian, chinese
 1. House:farmhouse is not to the right of House:gothic-revival##8
 2. Nationality:american is not to the left of Nationality:american##8
 3. Nationality:chinese is on the far left or far right##3
 4. House:gothic-revival is not to the left of House:ranch-style##8
 5. Nationality:american is not to the right of Nationality:american##8
 6. Beverage:water is on the right of House:ranch-style##1
 7. Pet:goldfish is somewhere to the right of Pet:turtle##5
 8. Beverage:almond-milk is between Nationality:italian and House:farmhouse##2
 9. Nationality:chinese == Beverage:water##1
10. Nationality:chinese is on the right of Pet:horse##1
11. Pet:chinchilla is on the left or right of Beverage:sprite##3
12. Pet:horse is somewhere to the right of Pet:goldfish##5
13. Beverage:water is not to the left of Nationality:chinese##8
14. Pet:goldfish == Nationality:malaysian##1
15. Pet:goldfish != House:farmhouse##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Pet         | turtle     | goldfish   | horse | chinchilla |
| Beverage   | mirinda | almond-milk   | sprite   | water  |
| House         | farmhouse  | colonial  | ranch-style  | gothic-revival |
| Nationality     | american    | malaysian | italian     | chinese    |

