.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
Job: dancer, bartender, doctor, writer
Cigar: cain, pall-mall, prince, tiparillo
Transport: van, airplane, trike, helicopter
Game: canasta, monopoly, snooker, backgammon
 1. Job:dancer is on the left of Game:backgammon##1
 2. Job:dancer is not to the right of Cigar:tiparillo##8
 3. Job:writer == Transport:airplane##1
 4. Transport:airplane is on the left or right of Job:dancer##3
 5. Job:bartender is somewhere to the right of Transport:helicopter##5
 6. Cigar:prince is not to the left of Transport:van##8
 7. Job:doctor is on the left or right of Job:bartender##3
 8. Transport:van is on the left or right of Game:snooker##3
 9. Game:monopoly is not to the left of Cigar:tiparillo##8
10. Transport:trike != Game:canasta##6
11. Cigar:pall-mall is on the left of Cigar:cain##1
12. Game:backgammon is on the left of Job:doctor##1
13. Transport:helicopter is not to the right of Cigar:tiparillo##8
14. Game:canasta is on the right of Transport:trike##1

